Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.record

Interface RecordAction

All Known Subinterfaces:
RecordAction.RecordPoseAction
public interface RecordAction
All the available actions that the Record stored.
Plugins can add custom actions and implement them using Record.fetchRecordAction(Player, RecordAction)
